      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would be a practical choice for someone looking for reliable transportation on a budget. The exterior shows some age with visible scratches and a few small dings, while the interior shows signs of regular use and minor staining. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it may require some routine maintenance or minor repairs in the near future to keep it in peak operating condition. It is a solid, honest car that gets the job done without the premium price tag of a newer model.",
