      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable ride that's ready for its next chapter? This vehicle is in fair condition and has been a reliable companion on the road. While it shows some honest wear and tear from its adventures, it still has plenty of life left and offers a great driving experience at a fantastic value. It's the perfect choice for someone who appreciates a car with character and a solid track record!",
