    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver or a great project for someone willing to put in some cosmetic work. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some fading in the clear coat on the roof, and a small dent on the rear passenger door. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and a small tear in the driver's seat bolster, though all electronics and climate controls remain functional. Mechanically, the car starts and runs well, though it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. It\u2019s an honest car that has been used regularly and is priced according to its current state.",
