      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by to check out my car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride for me and is still in great shape, just waiting for its next owner to take it on some new adventures! It drives beautifully and has been really well-cared for, so it's ready to hit the road whenever you are. Whether you need a dependable daily driver or something for those fun weekend trips, this one is a fantastic choice. I\u2019d love to see it go to a good home, so feel free to reach out if you have any questions!",
      "price": 34500.0,
