      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for the discerning enthusiast is this E46 M3, powered by the high-strung S54 3.2L inline-six utilizing six individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example features the sought-after Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. To ensure long-term mechanical reliability, the rod bearings have been replaced and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced\u2014a crucial upgrade for this chassis. The suspension geometry remains precise with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, providing exceptional turn-in and lateral grip. While the paint exhibits minor stone chips typical of a spirited driver, the powertrain is in peak operational state with a recently completed valve adjustment. It sits on genuine staggered Style 67 alloys wrapped in high-performance compound tires, ready for the apex.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Reliable performance. Clean title. Minor exterior wear. Interior well-maintained. All maintenance current.",
      "price": 31500.0,
